%% Adaptive retraining loop - data flow per stream sample.
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Stream as ELEC2 stream
    participant Mon as Drift monitor
    participant API as FastAPI service
    participant Det as Hybrid detector
    participant ML as MLflow registry
    participant Prom as Prometheus
    participant Graf as Grafana

    Stream->>Mon: x_t, y_t
    Mon->>API: POST /predict {x_t, y_t}
    API->>API: predict(x_t) -> y_hat_t
    API->>API: partial_fit(x_t, y_t)
    API-->>Mon: y_hat_t, p_t, latency
    Mon->>Det: update(y_hat_t != y_t, x_t)
    Det-->>Mon: DriftEvent (or None)
    Mon->>Prom: increment ml_drift_events_total
    Mon->>Prom: set ml_rolling_accuracy
    Prom->>Graf: scrape /metrics
    alt drift event AND not in cooldown
        Mon->>API: POST /reload
        API->>ML: fetch latest Production model
        ML-->>API: model artifact
        API->>API: swap model
        API->>Prom: set ml_model_version_info
    end
